As Astroblast rockets towards their base (dark avian) he opens a commlink,
"Speedbreaker, bring out the two memory components from storage, we will
need them". Over the commlink Speedbreaker's jittery voice can be heard.
"What, but those arent any use to us without blank". "I know" replies
Astroblast, as he closes in on headquarters.
